about.summary: A Component Library for Dash aimed at facilitating network visualization in Python, wrapped around Cytoscape.js

name: dash_cytoscape
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "dash_cytoscape" %}
{% set version = "0.1.1" %}

package:
  name: "{{ name|lower }}"
  version: "{{ version }}"

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 0cb0d26ba39273cecbb95ee61ceb9faebb71fd6617b7d5f245a73afb9c308444

build:
  noarch: python
  number: 0
  script: "{{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv "

requirements:
  host:
    - pip
    - python >=3.5
  run:
    - dash
    - python >=3.5

test:
  imports:
    - dash_cytoscape

about:
  home: https://github.com/plotly/dash-cytoscape
  license: MIT
  license_family: MIT
  license_file: LICENSE
  summary: A Component Library for Dash aimed at facilitating network visualization in Python, wrapped around Cytoscape.js
  doc_url: https://dash.plot.ly/cytoscape
  dev_url: https://github.com/plotly/dash-cytoscape

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - rluria14
    - oblute
    - adbeda
